    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"just exist\"? that's not living. it's just a slow way to suffer. i've spent my whole life being someone significant, and now i'm supposed to just be a shadow in the background? it feels more like a punishment than a life. honestly, it feels like the version of me that mattered is already dead. why should i keep dragging this shell around if there's nothing left to actually be?",
